{
  "stem": "23742.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But somehow or other, I got to know that she was Polish and that her family had come from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she said she have no family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "On the journey, we had no idea what were going to happen to these, these people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But as we got nearer to Brussels, to the center, we began to realize what was happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "As the trucks drove onto the square, there were hundreds of civilian people waiting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As the trucks came to a halt and we dropped back, these civilians just came forward and just took the first person that-- just stood next to them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I kept Sophie to one side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And later, I was able to get her into the home of some Jewish people that I had met while I was stationed in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she was a very poor, little thing, very tired and very frightened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And these people, whose name I forget, made her comfortable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were able to converse with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And two days later when I went back to the home, the, the story began to emerge, that indeed, she did come from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Her parents and-- I think it was two brothers and a sister, they were gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, she had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Although she only looked about 15 or 16, she was much older.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- I think she was about 25 to 30.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when it came to relatives, the only relative that she was aware of was an uncle who had emigrated to Australia in '37 and '38 and had repeatedly written to them to encourage them to come out.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He sent them money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they kept on postponing the situation, thinking things would get better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
